headline: ALLY Q4 Earnings Beat as Revenues Grow Y/Y & Provisions Decline
summary: Ally Financial beats on Q4 earnings as revenues rise y/y, provisions and expenses fall, and loan and deposit balances grow.

headline: PNC Wealth Management Simplifies Investing With New Online Brokerage Account Opening
summary: PNC Bank announced today that customers who use online banking can now digitally open individual brokerage accounts through PNC Wealth Management. The functionality allows clients to quickly and easily access a self-service digital solution for brokerage account opening.

headline: Is PNC Financial (PNC) Pricing Reflect Long Term Value After Strong Multi Year Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether PNC Financial Services Group is fairly priced or offering value at today's share price, you are not alone. The stock most recently closed at US$225.49, with returns of 6.2% over 7 days, 5.9% over 30 days, 6.6% year to date, 19.1% over 1 year, 58.7% over 3 years, and 87.1% over 5 years.
